snippet.title: Sonic R (PC) - Grand Prix: Reactive Factory Gameplay Playthrough
snippet.description:
Sonic R (1998)
Genre: Racing
Platform: PC
Developer: Traveller's Tales
Publisher: Sega

Playing Sonic R, getting all emeralds and coins and beating all challenges to unlock hidden characters. No commentary. Check playlist in the end of description and see all the playthrough.

0:10 - Chaos Emerald (Playing as Metal Sonic)
2:31 - Chaos Emerald (Playing as Knuckles)
4:46 - Coins (Playing as Super Sonic)
6:45 - Metal Knuckles Challenge

Playlist:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL_YL558gxlL_CglV4EXj0VFzWvsX9FxGq

#sonic #sonicR #supersonic
